你地睇到有卧底，等你地鬼打鬼，你覺得佢地真係派卧底唔比你地發現既，你地會發現到？<br />\n<br />\n下下懶醒話前線係黑警扮，對自己人傷害多過保護。一黎覺得受侮辱，二黎如果下次有扮示威者既黑警係人群入面話捉鬼，然後捉左依班前線會點？你估前線唔驚？<br />\n<br />\n我地要做既係比無限信心佢地，咁先係真正既保護，等佢地知道係人群入面所有人都支持佢地，佢地會好安全。只要前線做乜都唔割，就唔洗捉鬼。"},{"pid":"bdf7a1fadaa62d7e85042e6bb67b6bfe380ddd43","tid":1509560,"uid":237415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:32:48.000Z","msg":"good morning sir!"},{"pid":"a6e91c583be65118f4f4cb6082d12f8273a5af00","tid":1509560,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:32:57.000Z","msg":"小知識 - 原來機場控制唔只控制香港D機上落，<br />\n廣洲，深圳，澳門既飛機升降都會受香港指揮影響，搞到D飛升降唔到。。。。<br />\n大家千祈唔好搞到機場控制個班番唔到工啊 會好大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現有文宣集合 (Google Drive)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQri8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=dc4dead9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n請隨便使用，用自己的方法幫忙發送文宣出去，感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LoOsXdt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLoOsXdt.jpg&h=b1104862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">每晚10點</span></strong></span>大家開大嗰窗嗌口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當係抒發下或者互相鼓勵都好<br />\n<br />\n真係有人嗌㗎 唔洗怕醜<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fit.tsoi/videos/189596038709864/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffit.tsoi%2Fvideos%2F189596038709864%2F&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQri8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=23